desc: The Defender, with its long-held iconic history, is an off-road SUV available in three body sizes: Defender 90, Defender 110, and Defender 130. The Defender not only comes with AWD (all-wheel drive) capabilities, but also features a range of off-road electronics for enhanced capabilities. Depending on the variant selected, the Defender is offered with a variety of engine options, all paired with an 8-speed automatic transmission.
